name: 06. SLOTH
description:
6/7 from "7 Deadly Sins" collection.

I write weird sketches in the water; the daylight and your divine laugh, the curtain falls. The hanged clothes from days ago, and only three days in the lie of a lifetime, your look. At 6am your  dilated pupils there is nothing left, everything has been spoken, my mind is blank. Let's talk about the present that is driving us crazy and not allowing us to say hello; with your desires and my eternal ones, when the grounds burn I will not see you like I do now anymore, or like I saw you before, or like always. 
And as a warrior in his game I slowly kill my poison.

Full story: naranjabrasa.com
